features: 【54pcs Block Stacking Gmae】The colorful tumble tower set comes with 54 pcs wooden blocks, 1 pcs dice, and a storage bag. Each crafted wood stack measures 3*1*0.6 in and can be grown up to 10.6in tower when played. The Stacking Games bring everyone challenge and fun, adults and kids alike will enjoy this game, suitable for 2 or more players.

【Sturdy & Safy】The wooden stacking blocks game is made of high-quality wood and water-based paints. The materials have no odor, and no cracking and provide long-lasting durability. The building puzzle retains the unique texture of natural wood, the corners are rounded and smooth which makes it safe for your kids and family.

【Diverse Ways to Play】In this classic stacking game, players take turns rolling colorful dice and carefully removing a block of the matching color, then placing it on top of the tower to maintain its balance. If the tower falls apart on your turn, you lose the game. Additionally, toddlers can use the blocks to play with dominoes or build various shapes such as animals and vehicles, fostering imagination and creativity.

【Learning Toys】This rainbow stacking blocks game not only entertains but also offers numerous benefits for children. As they engage in this vibrant tumbling activity, can enhance their color recognition skills, fostering cognitive development. The game catalyzes creativity, imagination, and curiosity, encouraging children to explore and think critically, and promotes collaboration between adults and children.

【Ideal Gift】This stacking board game with a storage bag is ideal for family gatherings, parties, weddings and more, it will foster bonds with family friends and create memorable moments. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Awesome Improvement on an old idea
reviews.reviewText: How do you take a classic stack game and give it renewed life? Hello! Paint those blocks in vibrant colors!They just look more enticing, more exciting, and that draws kids and grown-up kids into playing more than the plain wood sets did. The colors also offer the opportunity to add more interesting rules to the game play. (Think putting "twister" into the mix.)Very cute, literally brilliant twist to a stand-by game. Awesome.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is a great tumble tower set! It's replacing one with wonky blocks and only three colors that we just put up with. The blocks on this set are smooth and even, and all a uniform size/thickness. They stack well and create a basically perfectly balanced tower that makes for great game play. The colors are fun and vibrant and they provide lots of dice roll options. Our old game went straight to the donate pile, this new one is awesome. We're totally pleased with it.
